imdb.plot outline: "Curvy Style with Timothy Snell" is a half hour docu-series that follows one of Hollywood's hottest celebrity stylists, Timothy Snell, as he works with celebrity clients and everyday women - and reveals some of the industry's best-kept secrets that help curvy women look and feel their best.
